description: Funny enough, it was only a few weeks back that we last discussed Dr. Keith Bell and the slew of lawsuits he has filed over depictions and/or retweets on social media of a passage he wrote, referred to as “The Winning Isn’t Normal” passage. title: Lane Kiffin Defeats Keith Bell In ‘Winning Isn’t Normal’ Copyright Case
